file_content.text: Talsa-ko! Watch as I crush the Republic scum!
Talsa-ko! Observe how I destroy the Imperial scum!
Diplomacy doesn't permit much bloodshed. How I've missed this!
I grow tired of your impertinence!
At this rate, you'll never stop my assassin from executing your Supreme Commander.
Your pilot friend screamed as I blasted him from the sky.
With your death, the Voss will join us!
Talsa! Remember this moment when you recount my victory to the Voss!
